user Green color Tape on your two fingers for control.
everytime when you move them the cursor will also move automatically 
and if you put your fingers close to each other and then it'll work like a left click and drag and drop.

install libraries wx,numpy,pynput,cv2

for wx use :-- sudo apt-get install python-wxgtk3.0
for punput use :-- sudo pip install pynput
for opencv :-- sudo apt-get install python-opencv
